comments: Sabonis (IND) places a hand to Jokic's (DEN) front on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Warren (IND) maintains a legal guarding position on Barton (DEN) following the pick and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Warren (IND) makes contact to Barton's (DEN) body during the drive however the contact is considered marginal and Barton (DEN) is able to continue along his path to the basket.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact to Barton's (DEN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
McDermott (IND) dislodges Plumlee (DEN) from his position during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) grabs and holds Sabonis' (IND) impeding his ability to get to the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact to Sabonis' (IND) off-arm during his shot near the rim.
Sabonis (IND) places his hand to Jokic's (DEN) back as he retrieves the ball in the post creating marginal contact.
McDermott (IND) and Beasley (DEN) engage and separate as Beasley (DEN) moves to set the screen.
Sabonis (IND) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Jokic (DEN) in the post.
Sabonis (IND) moves into and makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) body during his shooting motion that affects his shot attempt.
Brogdon (IND) grabs Barton's (DEN) arm during his drive and the illegal contact occurs prior to Barton's gather on his driving shot attempt.

Plumlee (DEN) has a resting hand on Brogdon's (IND) body during his shooting motion that he does not apply force with to affect Brogdon's trajectory on his dunk.  Grant (DEN) avoids making contact to Brogdon's head on his contest of the shot.
Turner (IND) makes contact to Plumlee's (DEN) body by jumping into him.  The contact occurs while he is dribbling and is prior to his gather and upward shooting motion.
Grant (DEN) makes contact to Brogdon's (IND) body during his dribble and the contact affects his SQBR.
Grant (DEN) makes marginal contact to McDermott's (IND) arm following the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) commits a take foul on Warren (IND).
McDermott (IND) and Craig (DEN) engage and separate during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (IND) makes marginal contact to Barton's (DEN) arm as he gets into a vertical position to contest his shot at the basket.
Barton (DEN) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
McDermott (IND) does not extend his forearm to dislodge Craig (DEN) as they both go for the loose ball during the rebound.
